ntent/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/2024_thetraitors_seriesthree_bbc_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在播出两季并在世界各地推出多个版本之后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-traitors"><em>《叛徒》</em></a>仍然是电视上收视率最高的真人秀节目之一。</p><p>第三季由克劳迪娅·温克尔曼 (Claudia Winkleman) 主持，25 名参赛者在苏格兰高地的一座城堡里争夺高达 12 万英镑的奖金。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-features/best-tv-shows-2025-stranger-things-bear-andor-wednesday-3826471">2025 年值得期待的 20 部大型电视节目</a></strong></li></ul><p>在城堡里，几名参赛者被选为“叛徒”，他们必须隐藏自己的身份并消灭“忠实者”才能获得奖品。然而，如果忠实者能够通过每日圆桌会议驱逐所有叛徒，那么所有幸存的参赛者都将赢得现金奖励。</p><p> BBC 去年续订了该剧第四季，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-uk-celebrity-edition-announced-3786092">九集的名人版</a>也在筹备中。</p><h2>谁在第一周就离开了<em>《叛徒》</em>第三季？</h2><p>开场一集介绍了所有 25 名参赛者，尽管他们在踏入城堡之前就经历了火车车厢的扭曲。三名参赛者不得不提名自己离开火车，不知道结果会是什么。</p><p>选择下车的选手是Alexander Dragonetti、Fozia Fasil和Jack Marriner-Brown，他们都被暂时从比赛中除名。</p><p><strong>被杀：尹律（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827330" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827330" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827330" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的尹律" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Yin-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827330" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的吕茵（图片来源：BBC 和兰伯特工作室）</figcaption></figure><p>由于叛徒们受到她作为传播学博士的怀疑和智慧的威胁，尹律成为第三季中第一个被谋杀的参赛者。</p><p><strong>被放逐：内森·海德（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827328" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827328" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827328" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg" alt="内森在《叛徒》中" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Nathan-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827328" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的内森 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>尽管圆桌会议上对叛徒琳达的怀疑越来越多，八名玩家还是投票罢免了 39 岁的房地产顾问内森。除了他安静的举止之外，这个决定所依据的证据很少。</p><p><strong>被谋杀者：基思·斯图尔特（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827333" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827333" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827333" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的基思" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Keith-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827333" class="wp-caption-text"> 《叛徒》中的基思 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>窗户清洁工基思被认为是该组织中坚强而可爱的角色，他成为第二个被叛徒谋杀的人。</p><p><strong>被放逐：艾伦·温（忠实）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827334" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827334" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827334" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的艾伦" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Elen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827334" class="wp-caption-text">艾伦在《叛徒》中被放逐（图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert）</figcaption></figure><p>在被其他玩家认为可疑，再加上她相信大多数叛徒都是“坚强的女性”后，翻译埃伦被逐出游戏。</p><p> “一旦你的名字被曝光，你就很难自救，”她告诉<a href="https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/articles/crrw4d1lxygo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>英国广播公司</em></a>。</p><p><strong>被放逐：Armani Gouveia（叛徒）</strong> </p><figure id="attachment_3827329" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827329" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827329" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的阿玛尼" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Armani.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/