/p><figure id="attachment_3827327" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3827327" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3827327" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg" alt="《叛徒》中的卡西姆" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Traitors-Kasim-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3827327" class="wp-caption-text">卡西姆被放逐让所有人都感到沮丧 图片来源：BBC/Studio Lambert</figcaption></figure><p>不幸的是，卡西姆不可避免地被逐出小组，因为他太友善了，而且——至少在杰克看来——因为他是一名医生。阿玛尼是在上一次圆桌会议上决定他命运的人，因为她莫名其妙地为他担保，让其他玩家相信他也是叛徒。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/the-traitors-season-3-who-was-killed-3827323">本周《叛徒》中谁被杀？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
